{"tha-ap163:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap163:0.2":"Suparicariyavagga ","tha-ap163:0.3":"Suparicariyattheraapadana ","tha-ap163:1.1":"“Padumo nama namena, ","tha-ap163:1.2":"dvipadindo narasabho; ","tha-ap163:1.3":"Pavana abhinikkhamma, ","tha-ap163:1.4":"dhammam deseti cakkhuma. ","tha-ap163:2.1":"Yakkhanam samayo asi, ","tha-ap163:2.2":"avidure mahesino; ","tha-ap163:2.3":"Yena kiccena sampatta, ","tha-ap163:2.4":"ajjhapekkhimsu tavade. ","tha-ap163:3.1":"Buddhassa giramannaya, ","tha-ap163:3.2":"amatassa ca desanam; ","tha-ap163:3.3":"Pasannacitto sumano, ","tha-ap163:3.4":"apphotetva upatthahim. ","tha-ap163:4.1":"Sucinnassa phalam passa, ","tha-ap163:4.2":"upatthanassa satthuno; ","tha-ap163:4.3":"Timsakappasahassesu, ","tha-ap163:4.4":"duggatim nupapajjaham. ","tha-ap163:5.1":"Unatimse kappasate, ","tha-ap163:5.2":"samalankatanamako; ","tha-ap163:5.3":"Sattaratanasampanno, ","tha-ap163:5.4":"cakkavatti mahabbalo. ","tha-ap163:6.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap163:6.2":"vimokkhapi ca atthime; ","tha-ap163:6.3":"Chalabhinna sacchikata, ","tha-ap163:6.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap163:7.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma suparicariyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap163:8.1":"Suparicariyattherassapadanam pathamam. "}